parameters: \N<Luna>Ahh~ Finally arrived~ It was quite a long journey~~~

\N<Sailor>Good work! First, you should head to the "Tower Dungeon."
There's a reception desk there, so you can get more details.
\N<Sailor>No problem at all! Well then, good luck~~!

\N<Luna>Alright! From today on, let's work together and do our best
on this island♪

\N<\N[2]>No... I'm just worried if we can really pay off the debt...
And from what I've heard about the dungeon, it seems pretty
dangerous...

\N<\N[2]>When I think about it, we're in an unfamiliar land with no
acquaintances, and no place to rely on in case of
emergency...
\N<\N[2]>Maybe I shouldn't have brought Luna-chan along...

\N<Luna>Oh come on~ It's fine♪ I'm an adventurer too, remember?
We've been on quests together many times, right?

\N<Luna>Even if it's the "\C[3]Tower Dungeon\C[0]," we can manage if
we're together.
\N<???>Hey, did you guys just say "Tower Dungeon"?
\N<Luna>Eh? Yeah, we did... Who are you?

\N<Syouta>My name is \C[2]Syouta\C[0]! The greatest adventurer in the
world! ...Well, in the future!

\N<Luna>A boy like you shouldn't be playing at being an adventurer.
You should know when to stop joking around...
\N<Syouta>Don't treat me like a kid-! I'm a splendid man-!

The boy Syouta suddenly became enraged and reached for
Luna's chest

\N<Syouta>Ouch... Damn it, stop interfering... I was just trying to
tease her a bit~

\N<\N[2]>She's my precious girlfriend after all♪ I have to protect
her properly, heh heh heh...
\N<Luna>Getting back to the point... Are you really an adventurer?
Syouta suddenly grabbed Luna's breast firmly
\N<\N[2]>You...! Why are you freely fondling Luna-chan's b-b-breasts!

\N<Syouta>So soft~♪ Such huge tits♪ They're bouncing around like
they're alive, whoa~~♪
\N<Syouta>Is this how women seduce men~ So lewd~~♪
\N<Luna>Th-they're not for that kind of use...! Anyway,
\N<Luna>I-I get it, you're a fine man... Now stop it!
Luna grabbed both of Syouta's hands and pushed them away

\N<Syouta>Tch, don't get mad over "just that"~ Big tits but a small
heart, huh~~♪

\N<Luna>(Hmph...) That doesn't matter right now... More
importantly... Are you really an adventurer?
\N<Syouta>Yeah, of course I am! What else would I be?!

\N<Syouta>I've even taken on the Tower Dungeon that you guys are about
to head to! So that makes me your "Senpai" here♪

\N<Luna>I find it hard to believe that a boy like you could go to
such a place...

\N<Syouta>Hahahahaha! As if you could go on an adventure with those
big boobs hanging down!

\N<Syouta>The adults around here might make fun of me, but I have my
own way of doing things. You shouldn't underestimate me.

\N<Luna>Yes, yes, I got it. Well then, we're heading to the dungeon
now, so...
\N<Syouta>You just got here, right? Do you even know the way?

\N<Syouta>...Geez, can't be helped~ The Tower Dungeon is due north
from here if you go straight.

\N<Syouta>Seriously, you guys worry me. If you want, I could take you
on as my disciples? I live in the \C[3]village\C[0], so come
and find me anytime! I'll welcome you~♪

The two of them proceeded in the direction taught by the boy
they had just met upon arriving at the island...
